Package ontologyFramework.OFEventManagement

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    OFEventParameterInterface
    This class is interface to implement the definition a parameter to be used during event computation.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    EventComputedData
    This class simply contains two field, moved during event parameter computation between the classes OFEventParameterDefinition and a class, called by name, which implements OFEventInterface.
    OFEventParameterDefinition
    This class defines the definition of a paramiter of a particular Event.
    OFEventRepresentation
    This class contains a basic implementation of how store initializate mechanism from the OFlanguage in data property.
